m, or we'd have the food consumption and such too.<br><br>Ninen of Saryrn<br>The War Council <p>Corned LipLocation of elusive "cow soul." Ingestion caused eater to stare into the whirling abyss of cow's true self. Left behind a gamy aftertaste and gibbering madness.I also eat Babies!</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ublazeodead.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Blaze ODead</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/29/02 8:48:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23086.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: evade success, needs upgrade, thoughts?</span><hr size=1> Naith, quick, edit out the sig before the mod's find you! :P<br><br>Sorry, I have nothing to add on topic <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulannellavelglarn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lannella Velglarn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.boomspeed.com/lannella/leaf.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/29/02 8:59:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23086.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.boomspeed.com/lannella/nextlevel.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: evade success, needs upgrade, thoughts?</span><hr size=1> Agreed, Naith, way-big sig.<br>----<br><br>Evade *should* be in sync with Haste.  It only makes sense that as we level and our damage output grows significantly, so should our chance to avoid the agro brought with it.<br><br>Evade should also be independant of movement.  If I'm getting pummelled by some mob who is the one moving me with knockback, it's not quite fair that I'm robbed of the chance to turn him away.<br> <p><table border="1" cellpadding="4" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" id="AutoNumber1" bgcolor="#000000"><tr><td width="123" height="101" align="left" bgcolor="#000000"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouselibraryreadonly.showMessage?topicID=98.topic" target="_blank"><img border="0" src="http://www.boomspeed.com/lannella/sol-hef-head.jpg" alt="THE LIBRARY'S ROGUE FAQ" align="left" width="89" height="89"></a><EM><STRONG><font color="#FF0000" face="Arial" size="2"><BR>&nbsp;</FONT></td><td align="center"><FONT face=Arial size="4"><b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6443"><font color="#FFFFFF">Lannella Velg'larn</font></a></b><font color="#FFFFFF">, &lt;</font><A href="http://www.rutabaga-paradox.org"><font color="#FFFFFF">Rutabaga Paradox</font></A><font color="#FFFFFF">&gt;&nbsp; Druzzil Ro<BR></font><i><A href="http://come.to/TheHighway" style="text-decoration: none"><font color="#FFFFFF">Nindolen d'Colbauth</font></A></i><font color="#FFFFFF"> ( </font><A href="http://come.to/TheHighway"><EM><font color="#FFFFFF">Thief of the Highway</font></EM></A><font color="#FFFFFF">) 52</font></font><font size="4"><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6443"><img border="0" src="http://www.boomspeed.com/lannella/headshot3.gif" width="60" height="60"></a></font><font color="#FF0000"><font size="4"></font><font face="Verdana"><b><font size="4"><u>Servant of Miragul</u><img border="1" src="http://www.boomspeed.com/lannella/miragultarget.gif"></font></b></font></font></td><td width="108" align="center" height="101"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafeho